{"tid":808242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又世界第一］取代紐約！香港擁全球最多「超級富豪」","createTime":"2018-09-06T07:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T12:10:54.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"9ceab1889c556e5fe1745bc76d9fb87fffe2a653","tid":808242,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕最新研究指出，香港已超越紐約，成為最多「超級富豪」的居住地。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，香港超越紐約，成為資產達3000萬美元（約台幣9.31億）以上人口聚集最多的地區，後依序為紐約、東京，法國巴黎也超越英國倫敦，成為歐洲第一。研究機構「Wealth-X」數據顯示，香港的富豪人數達到1萬人，增幅達31%，紐約的富豪數為9000人左右。<br />\n<br />\n報導中指出，全球富豪人數持續上升中，上升13%，總人數為25.6萬，坐擁31.5兆美元財富，其中以亞洲增長速度最為猛烈，主要由香港與中國最多，中國雖然沒有任何城市擠進前10名，但若以國家來看，中國的富豪人數居全球第三多。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2543044\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2543044&d=uPgkHeRgIihchTmC1i67d49%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=2109e69b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2543044&h=b4aceea9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2543044</a>"},{"pid":"3488dff20a8e47a834cf215215994dfcbf5d48ad","tid":808242,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:42:08.000Z","msg":"勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"046b92491d0a0b25d764d73d481c98697e3ede58","tid":808242,"uid":143241,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:43:13.000Z","msg":"香港不嬲都係世界第一嘅資本主義國家,喺呢道可以將資本主義發揮到極致！！！"},{"pid":"61d52aa2ff731c2e55432c5a21aea60961a7f7f0","tid":808242,"uid":14103,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T07:47:57.000Z","msg":"因為我地有最低工資保障計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我哋嘅工資永遠都被保障成為最低<img src=\"/ass